author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Porsche Names Its Top 5 Most Memorable Exclusive Models
text:
Just a week ago we saw Porsche detailing its best concept cars ever in their “Top 5” series. Now, the manufacturer is back with a new episode, here focusing on the most memorable Porsche exclusive models.
This particular list in turn highlights four of the most memorable Porsche exclusive models ever produced, in addition to teasing a never-before-seen exclusive. Showcased are various 911s that were produced in limited number, however, there are no legitimate one-offs.
To see what was chosen, and to get a glimpse at the new creation, press play above.
